{"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/FileOutputStreamRef\/writev(vectors:nVectors:bytesWritten:cancellable:)"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/FileOutputStreamRef","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/FileOutputStreamRef\/OutputStreamProtocol-Implementations"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"writev"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"vectors"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"UnsafePointer","preciseIdentifier":"s:SP","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":"<","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"GOutputVector"},{"kind":"text","text":">!, "},{"text":"nVectors","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Int","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"bytesWritten","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Sp","text":"UnsafeMutablePointer","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":"<","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@gsize","text":"gsize","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":">! = nil, "},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"cancellable"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/CancellableRef","preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO14CancellableRefV","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"CancellableRef"},{"kind":"text","text":"? = nil) "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"throws"},{"text":" -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Bool","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb"}],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"content":[{"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If "},{"code":"nVectors","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" is 0 or the sum of all bytes in "},{"code":"vectors","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" is 0, returns 0 and","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"does nothing."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"On success, the number of bytes written to the stream is returned.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"It is not an error if this is not the same as the requested size, as it"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"can happen e.g. on a partial I\/O error, or if there is not enough"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"storage in the stream. All writes block until at least one byte","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"is written or an error occurs; 0 is never returned (unless"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"nVectors","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" is 0 or the sum of all bytes in "},{"code":"vectors","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" is 0).","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"cancellable"},{"type":"text","text":" is not "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"text":", then the operation can be cancelled by","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"triggering the cancellable object from another thread. If the operation","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"was cancelled, the error "},{"code":"cancelled","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" will be returned. If an"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"operation was partially finished when the operation was cancelled the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"partial result will be returned, without an error."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Some implementations of "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_output_stream_writev()"},{"text":" may have limitations on the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"aggregate buffer size, and will return ","type":"text"},{"code":"invalidArgument","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" if these"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"are exceeded. For example, when writing to a local file on UNIX platforms,"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the aggregate buffer size must not exceed ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"G_MAXSSIZE"},{"text":" bytes.","type":"text"}]}],"kind":"content"}],"kind":"symbol","variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/gio\/fileoutputstreamref\/writev(vectors:nvectors:byteswritten:cancellable:)"]}],"sections":[],"abstract":[{"text":"Tries to write the bytes contained in the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nVectors"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"vectors"},{"type":"text","text":" into the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"stream. Will block during the operation."}],"metadata":{"externalID":"s:3GIO20OutputStreamProtocolPAAE6writev7vectors8nVectors12bytesWritten11cancellableSbSPySo14_GOutputVectorVGSg_SiSpySuGSgAA14CancellableRefVSgtKF::SYNTHESIZED::s:3GIO19FileOutputStreamRefV","title":"writev(vectors:nVectors:bytesWritten:cancellable:)","roleHeading":"Instance Method","symbolKind":"method","extendedModule":"GIO","modules":[{"name":"GIO"}],"fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"writev","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"vectors"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:SP","text":"UnsafePointer","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":"<","kind":"text"},{"text":"GOutputVector","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":">!, ","kind":"text"},{"text":"nVectors","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","text":"Int"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"text":"bytesWritten","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"UnsafeMutablePointer","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sp"},{"kind":"text","text":"<"},{"te